yodha ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2009 indian kannada action film directed by om prakash rao and produced by rockline venkatesh . the film stars darshan , nikita thukral and ashish vidyarthi in the lead roles . the film is a remake of tamil film bose ( 2004 ) directed by senthil kumar and starring srikanth and sneha . the film was released on 19 june 2009 across karnataka cinema halls and got mixed response from critics and audience . however the box-office results showed the film to be a success . this was the first film in the combination of rockline venkatesh - darshan .